item.title: Week.. Belt
item.description: This week has been nuts. I had a very nice time in class. It has been fun. I love to program. My company is insane, i went in and will get paid soon. weeee. I got a cool new belt. I think the most consequential part of the last week has been my relationship with kinnera. It has been a very exciting time. I spend a lot of time with her, and we have had the oppurtunity to share some special things with one another.
